'''重离子放疗'''（{{lang|en|Heavy Ion Radiotherapy}}），是一类利用加速到快至光速70%的重离子放射线治疗肿瘤的方法<ref>{{cite news|title=This radiotherapy utilizes heavy ion (carbon ion) beams.|url=http://www.hirt-japan.info/en/what/|accessdate=2014-03-06|newspaper=hirt-japan.info|archive-date=2019-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191121071557/http://www.hirt-japan.info/en/what/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

与现在广泛使用的[[光子放疗|光子放疗]]相比，它能够提供更好的物理剂量分布以及更高的生物学效应，从而达到更高的局部控制率和更低的副作用<ref>{{cite news|author=Agence France-Presse|title=Japanese specialist tests non-surgical ‘heavy ion radiotherapy’ breast cancer therapy|url=http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2013/05/22/japanese-specialist-tests-non-surgical-heavy-ion-radiotherapy-breast-cancer-therapy/|accessdate=2014-03-06|newspaper=Raw Story|archive-date=2014-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306112212/http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2013/05/22/japanese-specialist-tests-non-surgical-heavy-ion-radiotherapy-breast-cancer-therapy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

